<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ExamMaster</title>
    <style>
        /* General Reset and Fonts */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        /* Headings */
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #444;
        }
        
        /* Paragraph Styling */
        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        /* Indented instructions */
        .ch {
            margin-left: 25px;
            color: #444;
        }
        
        .chch {
            margin-left: 50px;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        /* Consent checkbox row */
        #consent {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-left: 25px;
        }
        
        #consent input[type="checkbox"] {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .imp{
            color: red;
        }

        #consent p {
            margin: 0 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #222;
        }
        
        /* Start Test Button Section */
        #strt {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        #strt button {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            width: 180px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #0077cc;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: monospace;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        #strt button:hover {
            background-color: #005fa3;
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }
        
        #strt button:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
            background-color: #004a80;
        }

        form {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        form button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2c3e50);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        form button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        input:checked{
            display: none;
        }

        label {
            text-align: left;
            color: red;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        input:checked+label,
        input:checked+label {
            border: 2px solid #8b5cf6;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
            color: #4c1d95;
        }

        /* for tick */
        input:checked+label::before,
        input:checked+label::before {
            content: 'âœ“';
            position: absolute;
            left: -30px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            height: 20px;
            width: 20px;
            background-color: #8b5cf6;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6);
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>JEE Advanced Mock Test</h1>
    <h2>General Instructions:</h2>
    <p>
      1. The clock will be set at the server. The countdown timer at the top of
      screen will display the remaining time available for you to complete the
      examination. When the times reaches zero, the examination will end by
      itself.
    </p>
    <p>2. The question pallette displayed on the right side of screen will show the status of each question.</p>
    <p>3. <b>Navigating to a Question :</b>
        <p class="ch">1. Click on the question number in the question pallette to go to that numbered question directly.</p>
        <p class="ch">2. Click on Next to go to next question and previous for previos question.</p>
        <p class="ch">3. Click on <b>Clear</b> to clear the response.</p>
        <p class="ch">4. By clicking on the option, your response will be automatically saved.</p>
    </p>
    <p>4. <b>Answering a question :</b>
        <p class="ch"><b>For answering Single Correct Questions</b>
            <p class="chch">1. Choose one option from the 4 options (A,B,C,D) given below the question, click on the bubble placed before the chosen option.</p>
            <p class="chch">2. To deselect your option, click on the <b>Clear</b> button.</p>
            <p class="chch">3. To change your answer, click on the bubble of another option.</p>
            <p class="chch">4. Your answer will be saved automatically on clicking <b>Next</b> button.</p>
        </p>
        <p class="ch">
            <b>For answering Multiple Correct Questions</b>
            <p class="chch">1. Choose one or more option(s) from the 4 options (A,B,C,D) given below the question, click on the checkbox placed before each option.</p>
            <p class="chch">2. To deselect your option, click on the checkbox again.</p>
            <p class="chch">3. Your answer will be saved automatically on clicking <b>Next</b> button.</p>
        </p>
        <p class="ch"><b>For answering Numerical Type Questions</b>
            <p class="chch">1. To enter the answer, input the value from your Keyboard.</p>
            <p class="chch">2. To clear your response, click on <b>Clear</b> button.</p>
            <p class="chch">3. Click on <b>Next</b> button to save your response ans move to the next question.</p>
        </p>
    </p>
    <p>5. <b>READ ALL THE INSTRUCTIONS CAREFULLY GIVEN ABOVE EACH QUESTION.</b></p>
    <form method="GET" action="/ques/<%= card_id %>/<%= id %>">
        <div id="consent">
            <input type="checkbox" name="consent" id="cb" required>
            <label for="cb">I agree that I've read and understood all the instructions and informations carefully.</label>
        </div>
        <div id="strt">
        <button>START TEST</button>
        </div>
    </form>
    <form method="GET" action="/users/<%= id %>">
        <div id="strt">
        <button>GO BACK TO HOMEPAGE</button>
        </div>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
